{"tid":27122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳癮君子想買冰毒 沒想到會收到冰糖","createTime":"2016-12-07T06:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T12:39:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"184812696d8641631115430be36ecba44ce24ef4","tid":27122,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20151206/large/1449374998_165b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20151206%2Flarge%2F1449374998_165b.jpg&h=98ae92a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n深圳一名癮君子早前在QQ上尋找同好希望購買冰毒，沒想到他會被騙。 <br />\n<br />\n這名癮君子姓劉，他透過QQ與一名同樣有毒癮的曾姓男子聯絡，購買毒品，兩人約定以1,000元人民幣購買5克冰毒，於是相約到一個大排檔，與石姓毒販交易。 <br />\n<br />\n三人如約交易，可是劉發現毒販給他的竟然一包冰糖碎，曾姓同好又逃去無蹤，劉十分生氣，竟然跑到派出所報案。 <br />\n<br />\n警方經過調查，將石、曾拘捕，兩人承認以冰糖冒充冰毒，已被當局刑事拘留。然而，花大錢買不到毒品的劉，亦因為吸毒而被警方行政拘留。 <br />\n<br />\n廣東《南方都市報》"},{"pid":"a1e67e48df7310a1592fae511e06933738f1832e","tid":27122,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:44:24.000Z","msg":"賣假野2個大獲D"},{"pid":"9650c2b4933110a4a40978887e0b65245d8e848c","tid":27122,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:28:56.000Z","msg":"條毒撚去到公安局點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 公安，我比咗成千蚊買冰毒，依家收到冰糖啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a935159b07d6118c6e95ff218670db52ffefd20a","tid":27122,"uid":6213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T07:31:31.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddc3fb8f715e749135bf9938c970f1b2b8dcff9","tid":27122,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣假野2個大獲D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n告販毒定行騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfbe294b81e5bb4a9977d0c1bd473cf7f584e26","tid":27122,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>賣假野2個大獲D</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n告販毒定行騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔係販毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb4854ea697048bd0236ee6588853d5bc8b5731","tid":27122,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:28:32.000Z","msg":"點告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c17eb6e0f91b98a2668b8af1825a302d268f12c","tid":27122,"uid":29846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:32:02.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25044ecbe5e3be0fff436b5eb04e0657ca3077fc","tid":27122,"uid":34762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"賣嗰個可以話一路都係講緊冰糖，係佢以為冰毒 之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}